类 AbstractPNNode<E extends AbstractFlowRelation<? extends AbstractPlace<E,?>,? extends AbstractTransition<E,?>,?>>

  • 类型参数:
    E - Relation Type (inherits from AbstractFlowRelation)
    所有已实现的接口:

    直接已知子类:
    AbstractPlace, AbstractTransition

    public abstract class AbstractPNNode<E extends AbstractFlowRelation<? extends AbstractPlace<E,?>,? extends AbstractTransition<E,?>,?>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This abstract class subsumes common properties of Petri net places and transitions.
    Petri net places and transitions are defined in the classes AbstractPlace and AbstractTransition
    whoch both inherit from AbstractPNNode.
    In detail, these properties are:
    • Name: The name of the node (unique).
    • Label: The label of the node (not unique).
    • Relations: Incoming and outgoing relations to other nodes.
      This allows nodes to notify other nodes about state changes.
    Besides basic properties, this class provides further functionality,
    such as extraction of child- and parent-nodes and source/drain properties.
    作者:
    Thomas Stocker
    另请参阅:
    AbstractFlowRelation, AbstractPlace, AbstractTransition, 序列化表格

                      java.lang.String name,
                      java.lang.String label)

        参数:
        type - The type of the Petri net node.
        name - The name for the Petri net node. It must start with a character of the range [a-zA-Z] and must only contain alphanumerical characters and the symbols -_.:.

        抛出:
